Smokescreen/Chordate:



Chordate stopped, poitning to a door where Smokescreen, Grimmler, and Rex 
were near, both weapons raised (that's how Yanshosh kind of described the 
latter two in his e-mails, anyways).  "Ok, stand guard here Skulletron.  I 
send a comm. to all of you later, when it's time to nab the intruder."


---

Chordate, running through the halls for the bridge, stopped suddenly as he 
rounded a corner, nearly hitting Feline.

"Woah!" he yelled, stopping in time, only a few inches from the female robot. 
 "Oh, sorry.  You were the hurt bot outside, how are you feeling?" he asked, 
looking her up and down.
